.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-generate 1  "generate 0.1.2" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-generate \- Run (or re\-run) LLM generation on an existing pack
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp generate\fR [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-overwrite\fR] [\fB\-\-api\-key\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-base\-url\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-\-model\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIPACK\fR> [\fIASSET\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run (or re\-run) LLM generation on an existing pack
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-overwrite\fR
Overwrite existing assets
.TP
\fB\-\-api\-key\fR \fI<KEY>\fR

.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-base\-url\fR \fI<URL>\fR

.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-\-model\fR \fI<MODEL>\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIPACK\fR>
Path to the DKP pack directory
.TP
[\fIASSET\fR]
Specific assets to regenerate (default: all machine assets)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.2
